{"tid":2139178,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【娛樂人物】入行逾20年終獲紐約視帝銅獎  陸駿光追夢犧牲愛","createTime":"2020-08-04T06:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T06:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4642c43bde75855616c1abcdde82bdcacf4bacc1","tid":2139178,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200804/ZRHHXNIWRQUHFMPTJAOJVAMLAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200804%2FZRHHXNIWRQUHFMPTJAOJVAMLAE%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd6QBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=dcb26dbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200804%2FZRHHXNIWRQUHFMPTJAOJVAMLAE%2F&h=d79132da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200804/ZRHHXNIWRQUHFMPTJAOJVAMLAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【娛樂人物】入行逾20年終獲紐約視帝銅獎 <br />\n陸駿光追夢犧牲愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3WUjv9iZc-ezk-gQgPKntH3XZ8Q=/640x725/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YQEBXV5V3TBW6AM5IXN2YPU43M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3WUjv9iZc-ezk-gQgPKntH3XZ8Q%3D%2F640x725%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYQEBXV5V3TBW6AM5IXN2YPU43M.jpg&h=6f225ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸駿光早前憑拍攝港台劇《星星的孩子︰魚蛋》，獲得2020年紐約電視電影節男主角銅獎。<br />\n<br />\n日劇《半澤直樹2》回歸，上月19日在日本首播已引起話題，前晚第三集更成為本年度劇集的收視冠軍。而「港版半澤直樹」陸駿光也有好消息，武肺疫情下不但有工開，更憑去年拍港台劇《星星的孩子︰魚蛋》勇奪2020年紐約電視電影節男主角銅獎，演技獲國際認同。陸駿光在娛樂圈打滾多年，捱過不少艱難的日子，當年為當演員，甚至犧牲一段三年情，幸好最終遇到太太陳曉欣，讓他無後顧之憂繼續追夢。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【多棲發展】撐港視被封港版半澤直樹<br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的陸駿光，入行逾20年終於取得人生第一個獎項，不過他日前接受《蘋果》專訪時，直言拍得獎電視劇《魚蛋》時，非常心痛，因為他在劇中飾演一名剛經歷喪妻之痛、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qPq9cQJ_MLYe_7ZH_-b8WOItW5o=/639x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UYKW65D3OIOYXXMVTCFRAS2JEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqPq9cQJ_MLYe_7ZH_-b8WOItW5o%3D%2F639x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUYKW65D3OIOYXXMVTCFRAS2JEY.jpg&h=8e39a081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《星星的孩子︰魚蛋》劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dEoHMb7pMOb_poMnpi2eamEkWKk=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F2D7HPAMH5TAQ3JCAPR2YVVIJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdEoHMb7pMOb_poMnpi2eamEkWKk%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF2D7HPAMH5TAQ3JCAPR2YVVIJY.jpg&h=a64484e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸駿光早前無懼疫情，與吳綺莉和周秀娜拍攝ViuTV劇集《太平紋身店》。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RbzqfUmBkxiJsKYAtGUYXSXkBDA=/640x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LPP6QBXKYXBAOBRASK2VUHLLYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRbzqfUmBkxiJsKYAtGUYXSXkBDA%3D%2F640x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLPP6QBXKYXBAOBRASK2VUHLLYY.jpg&h=863b8f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸駿光於2015年與陳曉欣拉埋天窗，他十分感激太太支持他繼續在娛圈中追夢。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hCJhwJ7IBo_wI5jUijT3F4BMpfI=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOCKPEP3HGAS4VPTIYJL44QVGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhCJhwJ7IBo_wI5jUijT3F4BMpfI%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOCKPEP3HGAS4VPTIYJL44QVGY.jpg&h=0435f4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸駿光入行逾20年，深感做演員疫情下開工沒有保障，一切只能靠自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做演員沒有保障<br />\n<br />\n談到去年逆權運動加上近半年的武肺疫情，陸駿光自言情緒起伏大︰「抽離唔到，尤其內心深處嘅痛，我有段時間直頭唔開心到周身出疹，疫情令我覺得生命好脆弱。除咗借角色去抒發同屋企做運動發洩，好彩老婆嘅陽光感染。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發脾氣離家出走<br />\n<br />\n陸駿光入行多年，多得太太背後支持，他說當年為了演戲，甚至連愛情都要犧牲︰「其實同太太拍拖前，幾段情都好傷，其中一段長達三年嘅異地戀，同女朋友斷斷續續只相處得半年，佢想我留喺加拿大陪佢，我當年喺無綫，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了太太，陸駿光說父親曾教他做人要忠於自己。陸父是傳統中醫，一生人都在醫館裏工作，他鼓勵兒子外出闖世界。陸爸爸在他十多歲時過身，但有段舊事令他畢生難忘︰。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n攝影︰林德雄<br />\n化妝及髮型：Kyo Lee<br />\n服裝提供：O.N.S. at Kapok"}]}